<p>I am trying to incorporate endless pagination to my site, but can't seem to get twitter style pagination to work.  I followed the django tutorial and I was able to get digg style pagination to work.  It actually loads the pagination and is communicating, but it doesn't show more when I scroll to the bottom of the page.  Here is my page,template, and view:</p>  <pre><code>from endless_pagination.decorators import page_template  @page_template('moody/endless.html')  # just add this decorator def about(         request, template='moody/about.html', extra_context=None):     context = {         'albums' : Album.objects.order_by('?')     }     if extra_context is not None:         context.update(extra_context)     return render_to_response(         template, context, context_instance=RequestContext(request)) </code></pre>  <p>about.html</p>  <pre><code>{%  load staticfiles %}  {%  load moody_extras %}  &lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt; &lt;html lang="en"&gt;   &lt;head&gt;   &lt;body class="no-touch" id='content'&gt;   &lt;div class="endless_page_template"&gt;  {% include page_template %} {% block js %}     &lt;script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-latest.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;     &lt;script src="{{ STATIC_URL }}endless_pagination/js/endless-pagination.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;     &lt;script&gt;$.endlessPaginate();&lt;/script&gt; {% endblock %} &lt;/div&gt;  &lt;/body&gt;  &lt;/html&gt; </code></pre>  <p>endless.html</p>  <pre><code>{% load endless %} {% paginate albums %} {% for album in albums %}     &lt;div class="box"&gt;       &lt;div class="boxInner"&gt;         &lt;a href="{% url 'album'  album.slug %}"&gt;                     &lt;img class="img-responsive" src={{album.img}} alt={{"https://i.scdn.co/image/9fd1d1fc621159e76379f253b4795a869632a332"}} style="width: 100%; height: 100% padding: 0; margin: 0; display:block;"&gt;                     &lt;a/&gt;         &lt;div class="titleBox"&gt;&lt;a href="{% url 'album'  album.slug %}"&gt;{{ album.name }}&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;     &lt;/div&gt; {% endfor %} {{ show_more }} </code></pre>